This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video captioning, which is a task related to visual understanding. It is also likely to belong to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it involves generating captions using natural language. The paper also proposes a novel approach using attention mechanisms, which is a popular technique in machine learning and falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses two prevalent datasets for video captioning, which falls under the sub-category of Multimedia (cs.MM).
